# Auto Deploy Slack

## TRIGGER
After any successful Lambda deployment that completes with a Function URL.

## PURPOSE
Automatically post to Slack whenever you deploy an app, providing immediate notification with the deployed URL.

## FULL IMPLEMENTATION
When trigger detected, read complete implementation:
```powershell
$content = Get-Content "C:/Users/mike.ullman/OneDrive - Vizio, Inc/Documents/Cline/Rules/full/auto-deploy-slack.md" -Raw
```

Or use read_file tool:
